//Family anamnesis - Mother

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Mamma MRI
When I select 'Positive' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Mother' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Breast carcinoma' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ovarian cancer' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Breast carcinoma' checkbox
Then Location dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year of life' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Ovarian cancer' checkbox
Then 'Year of life' dropdown menu is enabled